    text: "Tom Allen, Former Champion Pugilist, |\nand Ex-Detective Jack Williams\n| Among the Accused.\n Ex-Detective Jack Williams and ex-Cham-\npion Pugilist Tom Allen were indicted for\nmurder Wednesday afternoon by the grand\njury.\n\nWilliams is charged with killing Edward\nKassebaum and ‘““‘Bud’’ Pearce at Natural\nBridge road and Grand avenue before a poil-\ning place during the Republican primary.\nA warrant charging murder in the second\ndegree was issued against him and his pre-\nliminary hearing is still pending in the\nCourt of Criminal Correction. He was re-\nleased ean a $000 bond. «\n\nAllen shot Tim <Confoy to death in h's\nsaloon recently during a quarrel. He was\narrested and given a preliminary hearing\nin the Court of Criminal Correction, after\nwhich he was discharged, his plea being\nself-defense.\n\nThe final report of the grand jury was\nbrief. Concealed weapons are held respon-\ns:ble for the majority of crimes and a\nrigid enforcement of the law against carry-\ning them is recommended. Disreputable sa-\nloons and the winerooms are arraigned and\nbranded as the most dangerous institutions\noperated under the protection of the law.\nThe Excise Commissioner is requested to\nrevoke the license of every saloon that is\nnot operated in a strictly legal manner. and\neffective measures for suppressing the wine-\nrooms are suggested. )",
