    text: "Judge Taylor Denied Divorce to\nTom Allen’s Nurse.\n\nCircuit Judge Taylor refused to grant a\ndivorce to Tillie Hartgrove, who nursed the\nlate Tom Allen, former prize fighter. She\nsaid her husband, Martin, deserted her\nafter they had been married a short time.\n\nAllen willed her his property, except a\nnominal sum to each of his two daughters.\nHad he recovered, he was to have married\nher, If she obtained a divorce, it was stated.\n\n— ee Ree.",
